  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Oxygen-Fonts</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Oxygen-Fonts</application> package contains a
      desktop/gui font family for integrated use with the
      <application>KDE Plasma 5</application>.
    </para>

